comments: Source: https://docs.wfp.org/api/documents/WFP-0000153721/download/. This November 2023 estimate is the ninth update of WFP’s acute food insecurity estimates for the Global Operational Response Plan, which began in June 2020 and is covering 78 countries with WFP operational presence and where data is available. See also https://docs.wfp.org/api/documents/WFP-0000150316/download/
